Scripts to get reviews from restaurant of a given city (tripadvisor)

Depencencies
	python3
	bs4==0.0.1
	lxml==4.5.2
	requests==2.24.0
	urllib3==1.25.10
	tqdm
Create the folder data if not exists
	
Go to the code folder
	run 
		- python 1links_restaurants.py link_restaurant_city
		example:
		python 1links_restaurants.py https://www.tripadvisor.de/Restaurants-g187323-Berlin.html
		- python 2rev_links_restaurants.py
		- python 3get_reviews.py

Output
	A list of links and final text reviews are stored in the folder data
	Final output : data/reviews.txt (one review per line)
